## Home services across Baramulla

**Baramulla** is one of Kashmir’s largest service corridors — Panun Kaergar covers **Baramulla Town**, **Sopore**, **Pattan**, **Uri**, **Tangmarg**, **Kreeri**, and many villages in between.

### Services residents book most

Electrical faults, plumbing leaks, carpentry, painting before winters, deep cleaning, appliance repair, and salon at home.

Share your exact locality (for example Sopore Model Town or Pattan Market) so we can confirm the nearest available partner.
